ic understanding\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3310}, {\"ngram\": \"the other factors\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3346}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad taste\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But NBCU officials and Costas are rightly optimistic because Paris represents the beginning of a potentially terrific cycle for the Games.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3439, \"end\": 3443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 3496, \"end\": 3501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3233039095557754e-25, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Costas\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3464}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"a potentially terrific cycle\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3558}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris, Milano-Cortina (2026) and Los Angeles (2028) are fantastic locations for an American broadcaster, especially home-based L.A.\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3574, \"end\": 3579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3233039095557754e-25, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3607, \"end\": 3618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8279931608584405e-28, \"text\": \"Los Ange