 \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's iconic cities\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assuming Simone Biles is able to compete to the extent that she was in 2016, that should also help.\", \"from\": 5191, \"to\": 5290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5212}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 5235, \"to\": 5245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement \\\"I would still expect viewership to be far closer to Tokyo 2021 than to London 2012.\", \"from\": 5292, \"to\": 5391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5360, \"end\": 5365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.146060973762883e-12, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 5379, \"end\": 5390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6033815303432937e-24, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viewership\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As to NBC airing marquee events outside of prime time, we are at a point in the history of television when trying to embargo live sporting events is pointless.\", \"from\": 5392, \"to\": 5551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NBC\", \"from\": 5398, \"to\": 5401}, {\"ngram\": \"marquee events\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5423}, {\"ngram\": \"prime time\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5445}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 5457, \"to\": 5464}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 5468, \"to\": 5479}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5493}, {\"ngram\": \"live sporting events\", \"from\": 5517, \"to\": 5537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC has in the past aired live coverage on platforms with limited distribution as a way to maintain said embargo while satisfying those who want to watch live.\", \"from\": 5552, \"to\": 5711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NBC\", \"from\": 5552, \"to\": 5555}, {\"ngram\": \"live coverage\", \"from\": 5578, \"to\": 5591}, {\"ngram\": \"platforms\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5604}, {\"ngram\": \"limited distribution\", \"from\": 5610, \"to\": 5630}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 5634, \"to\": 5639}, {\"ngram\": \"said embargo\", \"from\": 5652, \"to\": 5664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Might as well make sure the live coverage is available far and wide.\\\"\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the live coverage\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One media-centric question is whether these Olympics portend a shift in consumer habitswith Peacock streaming every event liveand on-demand, including all 329 medal events.\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 5955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One media-centric question\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 5809}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 5821, \"to\": 5835}, {\"ngram\": \"a shift\", \"from\": 5844, \"to\": 5851}, {\"ngram\": \"consumer habitswith Peacock\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5882}, {\"ngram\": \"on-demand\", \"from\": 5913, \"to\": 5922}, {\"ngram\": \"all 329 medal events\", \"from\": 5934, \"to\": 5954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(NBC will have at least nine hours of weekday daytime coverage, expanding to at least 11 hours on weekends.\", \"from\": 5956, \"to\": 6063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NBC\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5960}, {\"ngram\": \"at least nine hours\", \"from\": 5971, \"to\": 5990}, {\"ngram\": \"weekday daytime coverage\", \"from\": 5994, \"to\": 6018}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 11 hours\", \"from\": 6033, \"to\": 6050}, {\"ngram\": \"